<P>
   BURGERS _ The first burger of summer is a pleasure on its own.
Grilled until crisp on the outside and still juicy inside, with its
hint of smoke, all the burger needs is a simple toasted bun. Says
who? We want to start summer with a bang, and Memorial Day is the
start of summer in this part of the country. The hamburger has to
be memorable. So we rounded up some favorites with additions that
will add big flavor to that patty of plain ground beef. (heller,
Dayton Daily News). 27.WITH ILLUSTRATION
</P>
