<P>
   INTERNATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   LATIN-AMERICA _ Q and A with Jennifer McCoy, director of Carter
Center Latin America programs, as the center prepares to monitor
Sunday's runoff election in Peru and election for all offices in
Venezuela. (Both elections are May 28.) Democracy in the region is
on tenuous ground. (Melvin, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL-LEBANON _ BINT JBEIL, Lebanon _ A follow-up and update on
the chaos surrounding the Israeli withdrawal from southern Lebanon.
Focusing on people for a color story. Developing. (Kaplow, Cox News
Service)
</P>
