<HEADLINE>
29 STATES PARTICIPATE IN MULTISTATE LOTTERIES
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By ROGERS CADENHEAD 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 1
<TEXT>
<P>
   QUESTION:.MDNM/ What multistate lotteries are currently being
offered, and what states do they cover? _ E.M., Irving
</P>
<P>
   ANSWER:.MDNM/ Multistate lotto drawings are offered in 29 states
and the District of Columbia:
</P>
<P>
   The Big Game, which had a record jackpot of $366 million March
10, is available in Georgia, Illinois, Maryland, Massachusetts,
Michigan, New Jersey and Virginia,
</P>
<P>
   Powerball is available in the District of Columbia and 21
states: Arizona, Connecticut, Delaware, Idaho, Indiana, Iowa,
Kansas, Kentucky, Louisiana, Minnesota, Missouri, Montana,
Nebraska, New Hampshire, New Mexico, Oregon, Rhode Island, South
Dakota, Vermont, West Virginia and Wisconsin.
</P>
<P>
   Cash 4 Life is available in the District of Columbia and nine
states: Iowa, Kansas, Minnesota, Montana, Nebraska, New Hampshire,
South Dakota, West Virginia and Wisconsin.
</P>
<P>
   Wild Card is available in Idaho, Montana, Nebraska and South
Dakota.
</P>
<P>
   The Tri-State Megabucks Lottery is available in Maine, New
Hampshire and Vermont.
</P>
<P>
   Eight states offer single-state drawings only: Texas,
California, Colorado, Florida, New York, Ohio, Pennsylvania and
Washington.
</P>
<P>
   Q:.MDNM/ One of my friends had a bit part in the movie ``Malibu
Bikini Shop.'' Where can I find this film on video? _ A.G., Bend,
Ore.
</P>
<P>
   A:.MDNM/ The 1985 film is out of print, but the retailer
CloseOut Video has previously viewed copies in stock for $5.99.
</P>
<P>
   CloseOut Video is a discount mail-order company that sells
previously viewed and remainder copies of videos, DVDs and other
products.
</P>
<P>
   For ordering information, call (727) 447-4147 or visit the Web
site www.closeoutvideo.com.
</P>
<P>
   Complete credits for ``Bikini Shop'' are available on the
Internet Movie Database at www.imdb.com. Bruce Greenwood, Rita
Jenrette and Charlie Brill appeared in the film.
</P>
<P>
   Q:.MDNM/ Where can I write to the actress Kristen Cloke? _ M.D.,
Moonachie, N.J.
</P>
<P>
   A:.MDNM/ Write to Cloke in care of J. Michael Bloom Agency,
Mitchell Stubbs, 9255 Sunset Blvd., Suite No. 710, Los Angeles, CA
90069.
</P>
<P>
   You also can send mail to the actress through her official Web
site, www.kristencloke.com.
</P>
<P>
   Cloke, 29, was a cast member on the TV shows ``Millennium'' and
``Space: Above and Beyond.'' She currently stars in ``Final
Destination,'' a film with Kerr Smith and Ali Larter released March
17.  &QL;
</P>
