<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    JUDGE MOVES TO BREAK UP MICROSOFT
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
