<SLUG> BC-HANSON-THISTIMEAROUND-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HANSON GOES ITS OWN WAY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MALCOLM MAYHEW 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
