<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    KIDS' MUSEUM STRUGGLES BACK AFTER HURRICANE
 &HT;    With KIDS-MUSEUMS for release Sunday, May 28
 &HT;    SPECIAL ATTN: North Carolina Papers
 &HT;    DUPLICATION ALERT: Moving in (l) lifestyle and (a) national
categories
 &HT;    By ANDREW MOLLISON
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
