<HEADLINE>
MICROSOFT'S `X-BOX' CONSOLE THREATENS SONY, NINTENDO, SEGA  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Business, Lifestyle Editors)   (This 425-word ``separate-buy'' story is from the May 2000 issue of
``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this article, it must be purchased
from the New York Times Syndicate's sales representative DEBRA
